Euthanasia in the Netherlands The Netherlands decriminalised euthanasia in 2002. Dutch doctor Henk Post reveals why he feels he won't personally help his patients to end their lives even though he agrees it shouldn't be criminal offence. Britain's female poker champion. Victoria Coren tells Lucy how she got under the skin of her fellow players Show less